oldSecurityDescription: Pandora A/S American Depositary Receipts - Unsponsored
Pandora A/S American Depositary Receipts - Sponsored
commentText: The Pandora A/S Sponsored program is being terminated Effective 2/5/25 COB. JPMorgan Chase Bank, N.A. will establish an unsponsored American depositary receipt program (Pandora A/S Unsponsored DR) effective 2/6/25. All of the remaining Pandora A/S sponsored ADSs shall be cancelled and unsponsored Pandora A/S ADSs shall be issued in respect thereof, at a rate of 2 Pandora A/S unsponsored ADSs for every 1 sponsored Pandora A/S ADS held. Cancellation fee per ADS:$0.05. Unsponsored Symbol: PNDRY.
